Thought-form of the music of <a href="/wiki/Charles_Gounod" title="Charles Gounod">Charles Gounod</a>, according to <a href="/wiki/Annie_Besant" title="Annie Besant">Annie Besant</a> and <a href="/wiki/Charles_Webster_Leadbeater" title="Charles Webster Leadbeater">C.W. Leadbeater</a> in <i>Thought Forms</i> (1901)</div>
